sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant React as React Frontend
    participant API as Express API
    participant DB as MongoDB

    Note over User, DB: Create Order Flow

    User->>React: Select Items & Click "Order"
    React->>API: POST /api/orders
    API->>DB: Insert Order
    DB-->>API: Success
    API-->>React: 201 Created (JSON)
    React-->>User: Show Success Message & Update List

    Note over User, DB: Update Status Flow
    
    User->>React: Change Status to "Done"
    React->>API: PUT /api/orders/:id {status: 'done'}
    API->>DB: Update Status
    DB-->>API: Success
    API-->>React: 200 OK (Updated Object)
    React-->>User: Refresh Order List UI
